```perl
open(my $fh, '<', 'file.txt') or die $!;
while (<$fh>) {        # read line by line
    chomp;
    print "$_\n";
}
close($fh);
```
**File I/O** uses three-arg open. `<` read, `>` write, `>>` append. `<$fh>` reads line by line. `$_` is default variable.

